code:
[MermaidChart: 65fcadc5-5b7e-46dc-90f2-b8c7a13927c4]

sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant System
    participant TeamLeader as Correct Team Leader
    participant Admin
    participant PublicDB as Public Network Database

    %% User Upload
    User->>System: Upload file
    System-->>User: File listed in "My Files"

    %% Submit File
    User->>System: Click "Submit"
    System->>System: Store file in Pending Review
    System->>System: Determine user's team
    System->>TeamLeader: Route file to correct Team Leader

    %% Team Leader Review
    TeamLeader->>System: View pending files (same team only)
    TeamLeader->>System: Download/Open file for review
    alt Approve
        TeamLeader->>System: Approve file
        System->>Admin: Move file to Admin Pending Review
    else Reject
        TeamLeader->>System: Reject file with reason
        System->>User: Update status to "Rejected" with reason
    end

    %% Admin Review
    Admin->>System: View pending files from Team Leaders
    Admin->>System: Download/Open file for verification
    alt Approve
        Admin->>System: Approve file
        System->>PublicDB: Upload file to public network
        System->>User: Status updated to "Final Approved"
    else Reject
        Admin->>System: Reject file with reason
        System->>User: Update status to "Rejected" with reason
    end
compilation_error: [WinError 2] 系统找不到指定的文件。
